column5: not good high and dirty at the saugeen.probably be a few days yet but there were some fish being caught at the damn.hit owen sound as well lots of jumpers but no biters for me the water level was a little low and pretty clear.also hit kincardine slow there too at the pier.iam skunked again but it was great weather.heard thornbury and meaford were doing well do your research before listening to me though.
